\begin_layout Standard
洛伦兹变换：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x^{\mu}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}x^{\nu}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g^{\rho\sigma}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\rho}\mu}^{\rho}\Lambda_{\phantom{\rho}\nu}^{\sigma}g^{\mu\nu}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g_{\phantom{\rho}\sigma}^{\rho}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\rho}\mu}^{\rho}\Lambda_{\sigma}^{\phantom{\sigma}\nu}g_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}\Rightarrow\delta_{\phantom{\rho}\sigma}^{\rho}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\rho}\mu}^{\rho}\Lambda_{\sigma}^{\phantom{\sigma}\nu}\delta_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\Lambda_{\sigma}^{\phantom{\sigma}\nu}$
\end_inset

是洛仑兹逆变换的矩阵，
\begin_inset Formula $x_{\sigma}^{\prime}=\Lambda_{\sigma}^{\phantom{\sigma}\nu}x_{\nu}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
矩阵的转置是交换行列指标，洛仑兹指标的升降是给行或者列加正负号。如果认为矩阵的转置会携带洛仑兹指标的状态，把行的正负号状态一并带到了列上（反之亦然）则，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(\Lambda^{\perp}){}_{\sigma}^{\phantom{\sigma}\nu}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\sigma}\sigma}^{\nu}\text{ or, }(\Lambda^{\perp})_{\phantom{\sigma}\sigma}^{\nu}=\Lambda{}_{\sigma}^{\phantom{\sigma}\nu}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\delta_{\phantom{\rho}\sigma}^{\rho}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\rho}\mu}^{\rho}\Lambda_{\sigma}^{\phantom{\sigma}\nu}\delta_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}\Rightarrow\Lambda.\Lambda^{\perp}=I_{4\times4}
\]

\end_inset

即，洛伦兹矩阵是正交矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $\Lambda^{-1}=\Lambda^{\perp}$
\end_inset

。但
\begin_inset Formula $\Lambda^{\perp}$
\end_inset

不一定等于
\begin_inset Formula $\Lambda^{\dagger}$
\end_inset

，洛伦兹群不存在有限维幺正表示，因为XXX（忘了）。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
洛仑兹协变导数：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x^{\prime\mu}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}x^{\nu},\text{so}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\mu}}f\left[x^{\prime\mu}\right]=\frac{\partial x^{\prime\nu}}{\partial x^{\mu}}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\prime\nu}}f\left[x^{\prime\nu}\right]=\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\prime\nu}}f\left[x^{\prime\nu}\right]
\]

\end_inset

也就是说，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\mu}}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\prime\nu}}
\]

\end_inset

所以相应地，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\prime\mu}}=\Lambda_{\mu}^{\phantom{\sigma}\nu}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\nu}},
\]

\end_inset

也就是说，
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\prime\mu}}$
\end_inset

像是协变矢量一样变换
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{\prime\mu}=\Lambda_{\mu}^{\phantom{\sigma}\nu}\partial_{\nu}$
\end_inset

，所以定义
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{\mu}=\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\mu}}$
\end_inset

，这是由于导数在分母上导致的，会发生指标的颠倒现象。
\end_layout

