\begin_inset Formula $A_{0}$
\end_inset

的正则动量为零，不是正则变量)
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Pi^{i}=\frac{\partial\mathcal{L}}{\partial\left(\partial^{0}A^{i}\right)}=F^{0i}=-E^{i}=E_{i}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec{\Pi}=F^{0i}=-E^{i}=-\vec{E}
\]

\end_inset

由此可以得到相互作用的哈密顿量
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{H}_{\text{int}}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{H}_{\text{int}}=-\vec{J}\cdot\vec{A}-\frac{1}{\mu^{2}}J^{0}\nabla\cdot\vec{E}+\frac{1}{2\mu^{2}}\left(J^{0}\right)^{2}
\]

\end_inset

在相互作用表象中，场服从自由场的运动方程，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\partial_{\mu}F_{I}^{\mu\nu}+\mu^{2}A_{I}^{\nu}=0\Rightarrow A_{I}^{0}=-\frac{1}{\mu^{2}}\nabla\cdot\vec{E}_{I}
\]

\end_inset

代入到相互作用哈密顿量
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{H}_{\text{int}}$
\end_inset

，得到相互作用表象的
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{H}_{I}$
\end_inset

(也就是相当于把
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{H}_{\text{int}}$
\end_inset

变换到了相互作用表象中)
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{H}_{I}=-\vec{J}_{I}\vec{A}_{I}+J_{I}^{0}A_{I}^{0}+\frac{1}{2\mu^{2}}\left(J_{I}^{0}\right)^{2}=J_{I}^{\mu}A_{I,\mu}+\cola{\frac{1}{2\mu^{2}}\left(J_{I}^{0}\right)^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

红色的就是非协变项。
\end_layout

